title: Elbow Grease Concentrated Vinegar 750ml
features: 100% Natural & Eco-Friendly – Formulated with pure white vinegar, this cleaner offers a chemical-free solution for various household tasks.​
Concentrated Formula – Provides powerful cleaning action; use undiluted for tough stains or dilute with water for everyday cleaning.​
Multi-Surface Versatility – Effectively cleans kitchen surfaces, bathroom fixtures, glass, and more, leaving them sparkling clean.​
Degreases & Descales – Cuts through grease and removes limescale from appliances like kettles and coffee makers.​
Deodorizes Naturally – Neutralizes unpleasant odors, leaving a fresh, clean scent without synthetic fragrances.​
description: Product Description Elbow Grease Concentrated Vinegar 750ml is a versatile and natural cleaning solution designed to tackle a variety of household tasks. Made from 100% pure white vinegar, it offers a chemical-free way to clean, degrease, descale, and deodorize your home. Its concentrated formula allows for flexible use—apply it undiluted for stubborn stains or dilute it for everyday cleaning.
